[size=3][u][b]Changelog[/b][/u][/size]

[size=3][u][i][2.00] - 2026-06-27[/i][/u][/size]
[list]
[*] Changed
[list]
[*] Repeat orders are no longer limited to a fixed list of supported order types — any order placed in the [b]Repeat Orders[/b] loop is now mimicked, including every one of its parameters, detected directly from the game engine instead of a hand-maintained list.
[*] A single [b]Repeat Orders[/b] entry is now enough to enable mimicking; the previous "needs at least two combined orders" rule has been removed.
[/list]
[*] Added
[list]
[*] In-game [b]Debug Level[/b] option ([b]None[/b] / [b]Debug[/b] / [b]Trace[/b]) under Extension Options, replacing the previous always-on debug output. Requires the new [b]Options Helper[/b] dependency.
[/list]
[/list]
